<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٧٦٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6106">مُسْلِمٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6858">وُهَيْبٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3721">ابْنُ طَاوُسٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2980">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«رُخِّصَ لِلْحَائِضِ أَنْ تَنْفِرَ إِذَا أَفَاضَتْ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>